Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.02,0:01:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第三界層的沙漠世界\N展開了旅程的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.46,0:01:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進入了由劍作支配的火熱村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.35,0:01:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是因為太熱\N令武一郎師傅倒下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.36,0:01:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外勇者之劍也被偷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.74,0:01:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我不能叫龍神丸出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.07,0:01:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過全靠火美子把劍找回來\N讓我打倒了劍作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.12,0:01:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們為了找出令第三界層\N恢復原狀的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.18,0:01:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由火熱村出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.17,0:02:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.37,0:02:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十二話\N瑪利亞妮的火燒記念日!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.87,0:02:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰棒、朱古力芭菲、蘇打水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.29,0:02:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再說了\N你令我越來越口渴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.92,0:02:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不行了\N不論走多久也沒有任何線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只令我熱得不行了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.33,0:02:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的熱度\N就算是我也支持不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能理解的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.13,0:02:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們真沒用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是精神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.12,0:02:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了,大人是風之子\N小孩是火之子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得好像有點錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨!我看見那邊有些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是雪糕啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.04,0:03:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是難理解的傢伙們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這…這個熱氣是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這比起沙漠更熱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.47,0:03:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是多惡達手下的城吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.57,0:03:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道\N但是個從未見過的種類呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.22,0:03:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們看來有點太輕敵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以再繼續\N讓他們成功下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也要在這第三界層\N收拾他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.99,0:03:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪利亞妮!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為這樣\N可以打倒渡他們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.13,0:03:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以無論怎樣也要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.61,0:04:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!到了午後沐浴的時間了\N對不起,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!古拿瑪先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪利亞妮大人\N我有消息給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.29,0:04:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接說了\N渡他們已到了這條村附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.93,0:04:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是時候\N讓他們見識你的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹什麼啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.11,0:04:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真對不起\N因為有不清潔的蟲在飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以只是想消毒一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.74,0:04:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消毒嗎?\N倒是你打算怎樣對付渡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.27,0:04:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要引他進這個城嗎?\N還是要在灼熱的地面上燒熟他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.40,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呢…呀!是了\N你可以引他們來澡室嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.65,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想這麼熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.24,0:05:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N整條村便像鐵板燒一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是方便的地面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這樣住在這裏的人\N會受不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.07,0:05:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連在地面上走動也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.01,0:05:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是火美子她真慢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來從剛才起\N便看不見她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.15,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平時她都會是最先來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.32,0:05:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子\N她到底打算幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,從天空拜訪之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.81,0:06:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是污穢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變得很漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耀眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.47,0:06:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐非常喜歡清潔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要少許不清潔\N我也會很不高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.82,0:06:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我因為想村民們也清潔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.16,0:06:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以把地面弄熱來個全體消毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.48,0:06:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!差不多是到了\N午後的超熱時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.87,0:06:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超熱時間…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.05,0:06:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別超熱時間,開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子她沒問題吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.29,0:07:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.92,0:07:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,沒有辦法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下很怕熱的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎樣才…對了,可以用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊,這樣飛過來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.61,0:07:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好呢\N古拿瑪!快去救渡他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.81,0:07:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒法子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.70,0:07:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是要人照顧的傢伙\N快點抓住我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請救救我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.92,0:07:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢…蠢材!\N不要一次過這麼多人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.02,0:08:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好\N這樣不清潔的東西便沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.02,0:08:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,領村內清潔\N姐姐真是個非常好的孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.49,0:08:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是很燙呢\N真是個過分的遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那應是我說才對!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.95,0:08:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真對不起,但是為什麼\N地面突然全熱起來呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天午前和午後都會有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.64,0:08:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被瑪利亞妮大人令溫度上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪利亞妮?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是支配著這條村的\N多惡達的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.40,0:08:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她有異常的潔癖\N把全村的溫度上升做全體消毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把全村做全體消毒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平時是很溫柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.58,0:08:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但一看見不潔的東西\N性格便會改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.42,0:09:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?這樣的話\N火美子她沒問題吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身是沙一點也不清潔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.60,0:09:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大事件了,要快點去救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,我找到好東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.79,0:09:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是城內有事聯絡的聲音放送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.36,0:09:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪先生\N你去了哪裏?古拿瑪先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是瑪利亞妮大人的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.99,0:09:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那她為什麼\N會認識古拿瑪的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.83,0:09:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…這個…\N我們以前曾經碰過面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.84,0:09:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你,我要你幫我\N快點來,古拿瑪先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.94,0:09:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,一定是引我去\N然後把我收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我反過來潛進去收拾她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.97,0:09:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.88,0:09:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼也開不了\N不知怎辦好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請吧\N謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.21,0:10:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你只是為了這樣\N而叫我來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪先生\N你可以靜一點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你為什麼會在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.14,0:10:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生也是\N為什麼會在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.47,0:10:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了!\N你和我一樣是來玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.96,0:10:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是非常有趣的地方啊\N我十分喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你啊!\N知道她是誰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.08,0:10:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.02,0:10:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道?\N她是我們非打倒不可的渡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.31,0:10:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐,來玩吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等…我不管了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是武一郎流踩高曉之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前在村中\N有踩高曉王之稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點名氣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.44,0:10:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,快點吧\N我很擔心火美子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,燒著了,趕快點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.90,0:11:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎?讓他們進入城\N和瑪利亞妮打一場吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!這邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.58,0:11:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點吧\N火美子被瑪利亞妮捉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.64,0:11:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在遇到很可怕的事\N快點去救她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欺負這麼可愛的少女\N真不能饒恕,去吧,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖不知那算不算是可愛\N總之上吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是瑪利亞妮也好\N這麼骯髒的人進入了她的城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不會就此算數的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.93,0:11:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩捉迷藏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.71,0:12:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,你在幹什麼?\N和我一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,火美子你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子她去了哪裏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.60,0:12:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪利亞妮大人\N渡他們潛進這個城來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.77,0:12:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他們把這個城\N弄得很骯髒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什…什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.75,0:12:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,把泥弄得四處都是\N真是非常骯髒的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.90,0:12:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不…不…不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子…你在哪裏啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.61,0:12:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵捉賊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道厲害了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得我玩得這麼高興\N你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.22,0:13:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在玩?是嗎?\N遇上了太可怕的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令你神經失常了呢…真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大傻瓜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.49,0:13:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很喜歡這裏\N我還要在這裏玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.87,0:13:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子去了哪裏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.50,0:13:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你便是渡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.60,0:13:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嬸嬸你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嬸嬸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.70,0:13:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嬸嬸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說誰是嬸嬸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你突然得幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.59,0:14:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟敢弄髒我的城\N而且還叫我嬸嬸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼嬸嬸你便是瑪利亞妮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又叫了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可怕的嬸嬸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,在下怒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.63,0:14:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.60,0:14:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美,真是美麗的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.60,0:15:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐,你沒有受傷吧\N來,抓住在下的手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要碰我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.30,0:15:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,她便是瑪利亞妮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是大冒險呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.11,0:15:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,你竟用這麼骯髒的手\N碰我的身體?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.30,0:15:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不能饒恕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,你又摸了她\N一些奇怪的地方吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.44,0:15:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下沒有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.87,0:15:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔好色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!這邊啊,見到你太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪,出口在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兵分兩路來逃比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武一郎和火美子這邊\N渡和我走這邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.70,0:15:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.69,0:15:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著到瑪利亞妮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃到哪裏去了?快出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪利亞妮大人\N渡逃到中庭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.14,0:15:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.08,0:15:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點用魔神收拾他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳,我不會讓你回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊?出口在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.20,0:16:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你知道反抗我\N有什麼後果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.60,0:16:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是出了一身汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.70,0:16:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活該\N接受弄髒我城堡的處罰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.80,0:16:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧,瑪利亞妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.00,0:17:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是無禮,定是想我殺了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恨!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.16,0:17:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是她自己在破壞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,我也沒出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她來了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的城堡啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.12,0:17:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟這樣做…這樣的話\N我要把你們全部殺掉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.52,0:18:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炎龍拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼力量?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.20,0:18:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能待在這裏了\N在下也要快呼叫戰神丸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.66,0:18:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰…神…丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.62,0:18:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,戰神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?感冒了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.62,0:18:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不好呢,燒到多少度?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.40,0:18:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這處是什麼地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很骯髒的婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是幹這種事的時候\N雖不知你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.49,0:19:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你救我出來吧\N我是瑪利亞妮大人的奶媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬? 奶媽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.80,0:19:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那姐姐是欺負我的可怕姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.12,0:19:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這樣的!\N她本來是個非常溫柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.50,0:19:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她被多惡達那傢伙\N賜予了邪惡之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.55,0:19:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是一天忘記了洗澡\N便說我不潔把我困在這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.17,0:19:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自那時侯起\N已有20年沒有洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.45,0:19:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪不得這麼臭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.08,0:19:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你,把我救出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.06,0:19:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,我用忍法救你出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了,龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.16,0:19:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.07,0:19:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,不封住這電刀的話\N會被幹掉的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.85,0:20:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍牙拳!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,我的火炎棍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,我不想這樣子輸掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.87,0:20:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼樣子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,又是那部魔神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.57,0:20:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.12,0:20:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我記著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這處交給戰神丸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野牛武一郎流交叉字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?已打完了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.30,0:21:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得我還把感冒\N的戰神丸叫來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不熱了,不熱了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.23,0:21:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太不可思議了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.83,0:21:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這畫像自古開始\N已在這城堡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.08,0:21:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極寒之劍和灼熱之盾\N是有所分別的,但現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.82,0:21:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩邊都在燃燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.05,0:21:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是\N有是什麼奇怪的事發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.65,0:21:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼這個灼熱地獄之迷\N也許便在這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.50,0:21:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這極寒之劍和灼熱之盾\N的所在地在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人可以很清楚\N恐怕是在…

